sketch.compiler.ast.core.exprs

Class ExprLambda

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.ast.core.FENode
      • sketch.compiler.ast.core.exprs.Expression
        • sketch.compiler.ast.core.exprs.ExprLambda

  • public class ExprLambda
extends Expression
    Expression that represents a lambda expression. A lambda expression is of the form

    (x, y) -> x + y

    The left hand side is a list of ExprVar and the right hand side is an expression.
    Version:
    0.1
    Author:
    Miguel Velez
